(3983,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=gFx5zgEACAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','Want to make a successful proposal in the data-dominated business world? You have to let the numbers speak to tell the story── The most convincing woman in Silicon Valley: Nancy Duerte In the era of big data, all decision-making is inseparable from data. But the data can\'t speak. How many times have you seen a briefing site full of numbers, you are in a daze, lethargic, and after listening to it, you are still not sure what the proponent\'s demands are? Fortune 500 presentation master, Nancy Duerte, analyzes the top data presentations of cross-industry and cross-border for the first time, and summarizes the innovation of Using Data to Tell Stories.'),
