(4956,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=Wtnu3Ib7A5oC&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&edge=curl&source=gbs_api','本書八卷，俱是作者對蔣大鴻《天元歌‧選擇章》注釋、詳解、旁證，以發明「渾天寶照候天星」之主旨。一改《天元歌‧選擇章》「二百年來，解人難索，註者皆差。」的局面。 後來民國三元玄空六法派談養吾晚年筆記《玄空本義》（輯入本叢刊），以及被譽為章仲山後第一人的民國三元玄空派四川王元極，都對本書推崇備至，認為本書方法是諸家選擇中「最合法」、「最上一乘」。後者王氏更撰有《校補天元選擇辨正》（輯入本叢刊）對本書內容進一步增訂、補充。 為令本書原刻本不致湮沒，特以最新數碼技術清理、修復版面，以原色刊精印出版，一作術數資料保存，一以供同道中人參考研究。【秀威資訊科技股份有限公司製作】'),
(4957,NULL,NULL),
(4958,'http://books.google.com/books/content?id=DY9QAQAAIAAJ&printsec=frontcover&img=1&zoom=1&source=gbs_api','This compendium is the culmination of an in-depth three year research project which considered how the European Patent Organisation (EPO) might rediscover and renew the basic principles underpinning it abd its inherent purpose. Over 100 formal interviews were conducted with leading experts, and from these the EPO dervied a set of scenarios for the possible future of patenting and intellectual property. These scenarios will be used by the EPO to address possible future challanges and opportunities.'),
